item.title: CVE-2021-3604|2024-08-03T17:01:08.315Z -- primion%20digitek -- secure%208%20%28evalos%29
item.description: Secure 8 (Evalos) does not validate user input data correctly, allowing a remote attacker to perform a Blind SQL Injection. An attacker could exploit this vulnerability in order to extract information of users and administrator accounts stored in the database.
